---
title: EIES University of Ruhuna
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<section class="flex flex-col w-full h-screen">
  {% include "./_includes/components/slideshow.njk" %}
  <span class="absolute px-12 py-8 bg-primary top-1/4 md:top-1/2">
    <h1 class="text-5xl text-white font-title">
      <span class="text-gold">E</span>lectrical and <span class="text-gold">I</span>nformation <span class="text-gold">E</span>ngineering <span class="text-gold">S</span>ociety</h1>
    <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-text">Faculty of Engineering, University of Ruhuna</h2>

    <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap mt-8">
      <a href="#about" class="px-4 py-2 mt-2 mr-4 text-white border-2 rounded cursor-pointer border-gold text-md border-md font-text">Learn More</a>
      <a href="#circles" class="px-4 py-2 mt-2 mr-4 text-white border-2 border-white rounded-sm cursor-pointer text-md border-md font-text">Circles</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="px-4 py-2 mt-2 mr-4 text-white border-2 border-white rounded-sm cursor-pointer text-md border-md font-text">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </span>
</section>

<section id="about" class="flex flex-col w-full px-4 py-12 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-background">
  <h1 class="pb-4 text-3xl text-center font-title">About Us</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-row justify-evenly">
    {% responsiveimage "./src/images/eies.png",
    "EIES Logo",
    "8rem",
    "w-48 mb-8" %}
  </div>
  <div class="mb-4 text-lg text-justify font-text" style="text-align-last: center;">
        Electrical and Information Engineering Society (EIES) is the main society within the department that 
        consists of the academic staff and students. The academic staff of the department facilitates to EIES 
        as an advisory board and the students lead each activity organized by the society. The goal of the 
        Electrical and Information Engineering Society is to upgrade studentâ€™s life in the department allowing 
        them to improve not only academic and technical skills but also their leadership interpersonal and 
        professional qualities.
    </div>
</section>

<section id="circles" class="flex flex-col items-center pt-2 pb-8 bg-background">
  <h1 class="pb-4 text-3xl text-center font-title">Circles</h1>

  <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap w-full px-4 py-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 justify-evenly">
    {% for i in circles %}
      {% circle i.name,
      i.link,
      i.banner %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</section>

<section id="committee" class="flex flex-col px-8 py-8 text-white bg-primary">
  <h1 class="pb-4 text-3xl text-center font-title">{{eies.year}} Committee</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap self-center justify-around w-5/6">
    {% for i in eies.committee %}
      <span class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-48 py-2">
        {% person i.name,
        "eies",
        i.role,
        i.img %}
      </span>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="flex flex-col items-center py-8 bg-white">
  <h1 class="pb-4 text-3xl text-center font-title">Contact Info</h1>

  <div class="flex flex-col w-full px-4 md:flex-row justify-evenly md:px-12 lg:px-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full md:w-1/2">
      {% for i in contact.telephone %}
        <div class="flex flex-row pb-4">
          <img src="/icons/call.svg" alt="tp" class="w-4">
          <div class="pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg">{{i.name}}
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">{{i.role}}</span>
            </h3>
            <h2 class="text-xl leading-none">{{i.number}}</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full pt-8 md:w-1/2 md:pt-0">
      <div>
        <div class="flex flex-row pb-4">
          <img src="/icons/mail.svg" alt="tp" class="w-4">
          <div class="pl-4">
            {% for item in contact.address %}
              <h2 class="text-lg leading-none">{{item}}</h2>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row pb-4">
          <img src="/icons/mail.svg" alt="tp" class="w-4">
          <div class="pl-4">
            <h2 class="text-lg leading-none">{{contact.email}}</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% for i in contact.sm %}
          <div class="flex flex-row pb-4 cursor-pointer" onclick="window.location.href = '{{i.link}}'">
            <img src="/icons/{{i.icon}}.svg" alt="tp" class="w-4">
            <div class="pl-4">
              <h2 class="text-lg leading-none">{{i.title}}</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>